### Get my Diablo 3 profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/d3/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{oauthToken}}

### Get Diablo 3 profile by BattleTag (replace # with -)
GET {{baseUrl}}/d3/profile/PAUKÅ TIS-2917
Authorization: Bearer {{oauthToken}}

### Get all Diablo 3 acts
GET {{baseUrl}}/d3/acts
Authorization: Bearer {{oauthToken}}

### Get specific Diablo 3 act (Act 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/d3/act/1
Authorization: Bearer {{oauthToken}}

### Get specific Diablo 3 act (Act 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/d3/act/2
Authorization: Bearer {{oauthToken}}

### Get Diablo 3 item (example item slug)
# Note: You need actual item slug and ID from the game
GET {{baseUrl}}/d3/item/corrupted-ashbringer-Unique_Sword_2H_104_x1
Authorization: Bearer {{oauthToken}}

